273
00:20:48,664 --> 00:20:51,372
Liam, you missed the whole concert.

274
00:20:51,459 --> 00:20:53,325
Okay? That's 20,000 fans,

275
00:20:53,419 --> 00:20:55,957
and me, and Doris, and the label,

276
00:20:56,046 --> 00:20:58,663
