passed away.

289
00:21:27,077 --> 00:21:28,864
<i>I just went to his funeral.</i>

290
00:21:32,249 --> 00:21:34,457
<i>Liam, I am so sorry, man,
I mean,</i>

291
00:21:34,543 --> 00:21:36,535
